/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/
/*═════════════════════╣ Start of About Me ╠═════════════════════*/
/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

#Matin-Pic {
  background: var(--purple-secondary-color);
  animation: MyPic-load ease-in 300ms var(--MyPic-delay-time);
  animation-fill-mode: forwards;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translate(0, 0);
  min-height: 71vh;
}

.Matin-Picture {
  user-select: none;
  margin: 15px auto;
  color: #ffffff;
  width: 380px;
  background: var(--purple-primary-color);
  text-align: center;
  border-radius: 5px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
  animation: float-lg-cardProfile 35s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.cover-photo {
  background: var(--blue-light-color);
  height: 130px;
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
}

.non-profile {
  height: 130px;
  width: 100%;
}

.profile {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 127px;
  height: auto;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid var(--purple-tertiary-color);
  padding: 7px;
  background: #292343;
  margin: -100px 0 0 203px;
  transition: 0.4s ease-in-out;
}

.profile:hover {
  cursor: pointer;
  transform: scale(1.2);
}

.profile-name {
  font-size: 25px;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin: 25px 0 0 -100px;
