/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/
/*═════════════════════╣ Start of Resume ╠═════════════════════*/
/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

#Resume {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

#Resume-items {
  list-style: none;
  text-align: center;
  display: inline-flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
  width: 100%;
}

#Resume-items li {
  display: flex;
  margin: 15px 25px;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-direction: column;
  cursor: pointer;
  position: relative;
}

/* CustomTooltip start */

#Resume-items .CustomTooltip {
  background: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  font-size: 13px;
  padding: 10px 18px;
  border-radius: 25px;
  top: 0px;
  left: 0px;
  z-index: 2;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  position: absolute;
  color: var(--purple-primary-color);
}

#Resume-items li:hover .CustomTooltip {
  opacity: 1;
  pointer-events: auto;
}

#Resume-items li:hover:nth-child(1) .CustomTooltip {
  top: -115px;
  right: -200px;
}

#Resume-items li:hover:nth-child(2) .CustomTooltip {
  top: -135px;
  right: -215px;
}

#Resume-items li:hover:nth-child(3) .CustomTooltip {
  top: -135px;
  right: -180px;
}

#Resume-items li:hover:nth-child(4) .CustomTooltip {
  top: -135px;
  left: -215px;
}

#Resume-items li:hover:nth-child(5) .CustomTooltip {
  top: -135px;
  left: -215px;
}

#Resume-items li:hover .CustomTooltip,
#Resume-items li:hover button {
  text-shadow: 0px -1px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
}

/* End of CustomTooltip */

/*styling Resume buttons*/
#Resume-items .btn {
  color: var(--purple-primary-color);
  background: rgba(168, 198, 222, 0.4);
  cursor: pointer;
  position: relative;
  outline: none;
  border: none;
  padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
  font-size: 16px;
  z-index: 2;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out, color 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.btn:hover {
  color: #dae7f1 !important;
}

.btn.btn-Resume-buttons::before {
  content: "";
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  z-index: -1;
  position: absolute;
  background-color: var(--purple-primary-color);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transition: transform 300ms ease-in-out;
  transform-origin: left;
}

.btn.btn-Resume-buttons:hover::before {
  transform: scaleX(1);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 6px var(--purple-primary-color);
  width: 100%;
}

.btn.btn-Resume-buttons:hover {
  color: #dae7f1 !important;
}

.btn.active {
  background: var(--purple-primary-color) !important;
  color: #dae7f1 !important;
}

/* End of styling Resume buttons */

#accordion {
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 1.3s ease-out;
  margin: 20px 0;
  z-index: 0;
}

#accordion.appear {
  opacity: 1;
}

#accordion .panel {
  box-shadow: -6px 6px 10px rgba(168, 198, 222, 0.3);
}

.Resume-click-open {
  max-width: 80%;
  border: none;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.Resume-click-open iframe {
  border-radius: 4px;
  box-shadow: 0px -3px 8px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

/* Start of Styling more-resume */

.more-resume {
  display: none;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  background-color: #0c0101;
  width: 100px;
  height: 140px;
  position: fixed;
  top: 34%;
  left: 0;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: white;
  padding: 20px 5px;
  writing-mode: vertical-lr;
  text-orientation: upright;
  border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;
  transition: 0.4s background-color ease-out, 0.4s border-radius ease-out;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 10000;
}

.more-resume-hovered {
  display: none;
  width: 100px;
  height: 140px;
  position: fixed;
  top: 34%;
  left: 100px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: white;
  background-color: rgba(48, 214, 145, 0.919);
  padding: 20px 5px;
  border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;
  z-index: 10000;
  transition: 1s display ease-out;
  writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
  /* Override vertical text orientation */
  text-orientation: mixed;
  /* Override text orientation */
}

.more-resume-hovered button {
  /* display: none; */
  transition: 1s display ease-out;
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px dashed var(--purple-primary-color);
  padding: 6px;
}

.more-resume-hovered button a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: black;
}

.more-resume:hover .more-resume-hovered {
  display: flex;
  align-content: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 220px;
  transition: 1s display ease-out;
}

.more-resume:hover {
  border-radius: 0px;
}

