/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/
/*═════════════════════╣ End of Contact ╠═════════════════════*/
/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/
/*═════════════════════╣ Start of Comment ╠═════════════════════*/
/*⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜⚜*/

#Comment {
  background: var(--purple-primary-color);
  padding: 5rem 0;
  min-height: 92vh;
  width: 100%;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

#Comment h2 {
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 30px;
}

.Comment-rows {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(161px, 1fr));
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 400ms ease-in, transform 300ms ease-in;
}

.Comment-rows.appear {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0 10px;
  margin: 5rem 0;
  transition: 0.5s;
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 40px;
  color: var(--yellow-primary-color);
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox label {
  font-weight: normal;
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox input,
.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox.textarea textarea {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: transparent;
  box-shadow: none;
  border: none;
  outline: none;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  padding: 0 10px;
  z-index: 1;
  color: var(--purple-primary-color);
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox .Comment-text {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  line-height: 40px;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  padding: 0 10px;
  display: block;
  transition: 0.5s;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.Comment-rows
  .Comment-form
  .Comment-InputBox
  input:not([required]):not(:placeholder-shown)
  + .Comment-text,
.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox input:focus + .Comment-text,
.Comment-rows
  .Comment-form
  .Comment-InputBox
  input[required]:valid
  + .Comment-text,
.Comment-rows
  .Comment-form
  .Comment-InputBox
  input[type="email"]:not(:placeholder-shown)
  + .Comment-text {
  top: -35px;
  right: -10px;
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox .Comment-Line {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--yellow-primary-color);
  transition: 0.5s;
  border-radius: 2px;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.Comment-rows
  .Comment-form
  .Comment-InputBox
  input:not([required]):not(:placeholder-shown)
  ~ .Comment-Line,
.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox input:focus ~ .Comment-Line,
.Comment-rows
  .Comment-form
  .Comment-InputBox
  input[required]:valid
  ~ .Comment-Line,
.Comment-rows
  .Comment-form
  .Comment-InputBox
  input[type="email"]:not(:placeholder-shown)
  ~ .Comment-Line {
  height: 100%;
}

/*textarea*/
.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox.textarea {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100px;
  position: relative;
  padding: 10px 0;
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox.textarea textarea {
  height: 100%;
  resize: none;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox textarea:focus + .Comment-text,
.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox textarea:valid + .Comment-text {
  top: -35px;
  right: -10px;
}

.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox textarea:focus ~ .Comment-Line,
.Comment-rows .Comment-form .Comment-InputBox textarea:valid ~ .Comment-Line {
  height: 100%;
}

/*send button*/
.Comment-form-Button {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  margin: 6rem auto 0;
}

.Comment-form-Button button {
  position: relative;
  text-decoration: none;
  width: 200px;
  padding: 2rem 5rem;
  display: block;
  text-align: center;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 3px;
  border: none;
  outline: none;
  background: none;
}

.Comment-form-Button button:hover .liquid,
.Comment-form-Button button:focus .liquid {
  top: -120px;
}

.Comment-form-Button button span {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  color: #fff;
}

.Comment-form-Button button .liquid {
  position: absolute;
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
  left: 0;
  top: -80px;
  background: #0039fa;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  transition: 0.5s;
}

.Comment-form-Button button .liquid::before,
.Comment-form-Button button .liquid::after {
  position: absolute;
  content: "";
  width: 200%;
  height: 200%;
  top: 0;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -75%);
}

.Comment-form-Button button .liquid::before {
  border-radius: 45%;
  background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 1);
  animation: CommentButton 5s linear infinite;
}

.Comment-form-Button button .liquid::after {
  border-radius: 40%;
  background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.5);
  animation: CommentButton 10s linear infinite;
}

@media (max-width: 210px) {
  .Comment-form-Button button {
    margin: auto 10px;
  }
}

@keyframes CommentButton {
  0% {
    transform: translate(-50%, -75%) rotate(0deg);
  }

  100% {
    transform: translate(-50%, -75%) rotate(360deg);
  }
}

